  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Trim the asparagus to uniform lengths",
    "Thread the asparagus onto skewers",
    "In a small bowl, mix together olive oil, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, black pepper, and chili flakes",
    "Brush the mixture onto the asparagus",
    "Grill the asparagus for 12 minutes, turning occasionally",
    "Squeeze lemon juice over the asparagus during the last 2 minutes of grilling",
    "Remove the asparagus from the grill and serve immediately"
